data.description: One has the option to assume the current loan w/ an all-time low interest rate of 3.125%! Potentially saving you hundred(s) per month, & thousands over time! Postcard views, and a composite deck perfect for outdoor enjoyment! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom manufactured home is perfectly situated on 6+ acres. Cross the threshold into a warm welcome that includes neutral decor, newer flooring, and newly installed baseboards. The spacious kitchen offers plenty of storage space, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of counter space offering culinary promise. Exteriors include a dependable composite deck and a breezy covered front porch. Easy commute to centers of employment means more time to enjoy the enviable mountain views. You'll thank yourself for getting your offer in early.
